{"type":null,"faqId":47748,"title":"Weather data is inaccurate","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span>Go to </span><span class=\"s2\">Weather</span><span>. For EMUI 2.0 or 2.3, select </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177039\" style=\"width:0.30208334in;height:0.22083333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> to update weather data. For EMUI 3.0, drag your finger downwards to update weather data.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177040\" style=\"width:0.59305555in;height:0.16180556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>Before updating weather data, please ensure that your phone has a mobile data or Wi-Fi connection.</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>If weather data is still inaccurate after updating, it could be because data for that weather app has not yet been updated. Please try updating later.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>Download other similar weather apps and see if weather data is accurate.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177041\" style=\"width:0.59305555in;height:0.16180556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>Apps cannot provide entirely reliable weather data. It is recommended that you consult the data provided by the local meteorological bureau.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"3292","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445479606000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-L03,Holly-U19,Jazz-L09,Jazz-L11,Y220-U00,Y330-U01,Y336-U02,Y360-U61,Y520-U22","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"inaccurate weather, refresh weather","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}